## 🐛 Bugs & Issues Found

### Critical
1. **Modal HTML is broken** — The `cloud-modal` div is not properly opened; the `<div class="modal" id="cloud-modal">` tag and its `<div class="modal-header">` close tag are missing. The `data-modal` and close-btn logic will silently fail for the Cloud card.
2. **`modal-overlay` div is missing** from [index.html](file:///c:/Users/Yash/OneDrive/Desktop/GIT/INFRBUILD/index.html) — [script.js](file:///c:/Users/Yash/OneDrive/Desktop/GIT/INFRBUILD/script.js) calls `document.getElementById("modal-overlay")` but there is no `<div id="modal-overlay">` in the HTML. This causes a JS crash that breaks **all** modals.
3. **Formspree URL is placeholder** — `action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORM_ID"` — form submissions will always fail.
4. **Inline `<style>` block inside `<section>`** (lines 206–220 in index.html) — bad practice; should be moved to [style.css](file:///c:/Users/Yash/OneDrive/Desktop/GIT/INFRBUILD/style.css).
5. **`.spinner` keyframe bug** — the `spin` animation's `transform` conflicts with the absolute `translate(-50%,-50%)`. Spinner will appear in wrong position mid-animation.

### Medium
6. **Mobile nav is hidden with CSS `display:none`** at < 900px but no hamburger menu replacement exists — mobile users have no navigation.
7. **Only 1 of 4 product pages exists** ([cloud.html](file:///c:/Users/Yash/OneDrive/Desktop/GIT/INFRBUILD/products/cloud.html)) — clicking on Data, AI, or Web cards won't navigate anywhere.
8. **`--card` CSS variable** used in `.about-card` but defined only in a `@media (prefers-color-scheme: light)` block, meaning it's `undefined` in dark mode by default.
9. **Duplicate CSS rules** — `.expertise-grid` and `.product-card` are defined twice, causing specificity confusion.
10. **[README.md](file:///c:/Users/Yash/OneDrive/Desktop/GIT/INFRBUILD/README.md) is empty** (only 11 bytes).

### Minor
11. **No `<meta description>`** — bad for SEO / social sharing.
12. **No favicon** configured.
13. **[contact.html](file:///c:/Users/Yash/OneDrive/Desktop/GIT/INFRBUILD/contact.html) has no [script.js](file:///c:/Users/Yash/OneDrive/Desktop/GIT/INFRBUILD/script.js)** linked — the contact form's loading spinner and success message will not work.
14. **`hero-actions` buttons** link to `#contact` which doesn't exist on the page — should link to [contact.html](file:///c:/Users/Yash/OneDrive/Desktop/GIT/INFRBUILD/contact.html).

