## 🚀 Improvement Roadmap (Prioritized)

### 🔥 Phase 1 — Fix the Basics (Critical Bugs)

- [ ] **Fix modal HTML** — wrap each modal in proper `<div class="modal" id="...">` and add `<div id="modal-overlay" class="modal-overlay"></div>` to [index.html](file:///c:/Users/Yash/OneDrive/Desktop/GIT/INFRBUILD/index.html)
- [ ] **Fix `.spinner` CSS** — use `transform-origin` approach to avoid conflict
- [ ] **Add [script.js](file:///c:/Users/Yash/OneDrive/Desktop/GIT/INFRBUILD/script.js)** to [contact.html](file:///c:/Users/Yash/OneDrive/Desktop/GIT/INFRBUILD/contact.html)
- [ ] **Replace Formspree placeholder ID** with real one
- [ ] **Move inline `<style>`** from HTML to CSS
- [ ] **Add `--card` variable** to the `:root` default (dark) block
- [ ] **Fix hero CTA** (`#contact` → [contact.html](file:///c:/Users/Yash/OneDrive/Desktop/GIT/INFRBUILD/contact.html))

---

### ✨ Phase 2 — Major Features to Add

#### 1. 📱 Mobile Hamburger Menu
A collapsible slide-in sidebar/drawer for mobile users. Currently there is no navigation at all on mobile.

#### 2. 🗂️ Products Pages (3 missing)
Create `products/data.html`, `products/ai.html`, `products/web.html` with detailed feature breakdowns, tech stacks, and CTAs.

#### 3. 🌟 Testimonials / Social Proof Section
Add a client testimonials carousel between Case Studies and Leadership — key for startup credibility.

#### 4. 📊 Stats / Impact Counter Section
Animated number counters (e.g., "3 Products Built", "2 Co-Founders", "100% Client Satisfaction") that count up on scroll.

#### 5. 🗓️ Services / Pricing Section
A clear 3-column pricing/tier card that shows what InfraBuild offers at different engagement levels (Consultation / Build / Scale).

#### 6. 📝 Blog / Insights Section (Advanced)
A minimal blog for thought leadership (can be static HTML files or connected to a CMS like Contentful or Notion API).

#### 7. 🔗 Projects Showcase Page
A dedicated `projects.html` with cards showing each project with screenshots, tech stack badges, GitHub links, and live demo links.

#### 8. 🤖 AI Chat Widget
A floating chat bubble that uses a free AI API (like Gemini or OpenAI) so visitors can ask about InfraBuild services.

#### 9. 🔔 Newsletter Signup
A footer or popup form to collect email leads (Mailchimp / ConvertKit integration).

#### 10. 🍪 Cookie Banner + Privacy Policy
Required for any production website.

