### 🎨 Phase 3 — Design Upgrades

| Upgrade | Description |
|---|---|
| **Particle / mesh background** | Replace static gradient with an animated particle mesh (tsParticles or pure CSS) |
| **Animated gradient text** | Hero heading with animated gradient colors cycling |
| **Custom cursor** | Branded custom cursor with glow on hover |
| **Scroll progress bar** | Thin line at top of page showing scroll progress |
| **Page transitions** | Smooth fade-in on page load, fade-out on navigation |
| **Lottie animations** | Replace emoji icons with Lottie JSON animations for Cloud, Data, AI, Web cards |
| **Loading screen** | Branded intro animation before page loads |

