### ⚙️ Phase 4 — Technical / SEO Improvements

| Item | Action |
|---|---|
| Add `<meta name="description">` | Write compelling 160-char description |
| Add Open Graph tags | For LinkedIn/Twitter sharing previews |
| Add a `favicon.ico` | Using InfraBuild logo |
| Add `sitemap.xml` | For search engines |
| Lazy-load images | `loading="lazy"` on all images |
| Convert images to WebP | Reduce load time (JPEG images are 150–260KB each) |
| Add `robots.txt` | Allow/disallow crawlers |
| Add Google Analytics or Plausible | Track visitors |

