## 💡 Summary

Your InfraBuild site has a **solid foundation** — good dark theme, nice animations, clean layout. But it has several **critical bugs** (broken modals, missing overlay div, no mobile nav) that need fixing first. After that, the biggest opportunity is building a **Projects Showcase page** since your goal is to introduce your products and projects to visitors. Then focus on completion: product detail pages, stats, testimonials, and mobile responsiveness.
